  "texts": [
    "Then in Sect. 4, we examine different types of features that are extracted and used in the literature for disinformation detection.",
    "We explore different GNN-based techniques proposed recently for disinformation detection, in Sect. 5.",
    "We describe the datasets commonly used to evaluate algorithms in Sect. 6.",
    "We introduce ongoing problems and outline possible future research directions, in Sect. 7.",
    "Finally, the paper is concluded in Sect. 8."
  ]
